Nutrient data for: CADBURY DRINKING CHOCOLATE HOT CHOCOLATE-LIQUID, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300749729

Ingredients: Fat-reduced cocoa powder (28%), dried whey (from MILK), dried skimmed MILK, inulin, milk chocolate (6%) (MILK, sugar, cocoa butter, cocoa mass, vegetable fats (palm, shea), emulsifiers (E442, sunflower lecithin), flavourings), glucose syrup, palm oil, salt, thickener (E466), anti-caking agent (E551), MILK proteins, flavourings, sweetener (sucralose), emulsifier (E471). Cocoa, sugar: traded in compliance with Fairtrade Standards, total 30%.
